<h2>Netflix Class</h2>
<p>Along with this helper, you will find the <b>Netflix</b> class, which is as an example on how wrap up the OData helper to define your own custom helper operations against a specific OData Producer, in this case <a href="http://developer.netflix.com/docs/OData_Catalog">NetFlix</a>. Continue extending this class by adding more Netflix queries!</p>
